        "content": "### Observability Stack Notes\n\n- `Prometheus`, `Grafana`, `Loki`, `Tempo`, and `Alloy` are now scraped into Prometheus for stack-level health panels.\n- Loki and Tempo datasources are provisioned in Grafana.\n- Alloy currently forwards traces to Tempo. It does **not** yet ship application logs to Loki in the current repo configuration, so Loki-specific dashboards will remain mostly empty until log shipping is added.",
